# TSDoc Commenting

When the user asks to add comments about file contents, write comments in TSDoc format.

- Use `/** ... */` doc-comment blocks
- Include `@remarks` for file/module-level summaries
- Include `@param` and `@returns` on every function/method
- Use `@example` when a usage snippet would clarify intent
- Do not add redundant comments that restate obvious code